  "text": "The supercritical process was carried out in a static mode to achieve the inclusion of the drug in the cyclodextrin. The apparatus is equipped with a volumetric pump, a 50 mL vessel, and a depressurisation system. The vessel is positioned inside an oven, which maintained all the system at constant temperature. Further details of the apparatus can be found elsewhere [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
